title: Street Organics
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Raw, Juice bar, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe offering labeled vegan meals, snacks and hot & cold drinks with plant milk options including soy, oat, and rice, as well as house-made coconut, almond, and cashew. Raw vegan high tea available daily for tables of 4-30 people and high tea group sittings are held once per month (booking required).
